quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  20,105,"Ke kaloku bakubuza ngeentaba: Yithi, “INkosi yam Iza kuziqhushumbisa, Izichithe zibe ngamasuntswana othuli"
  20,106,Ize Izishiye zilele tyaba (zingamathafa)
  20,107,“Akuyi kubona nto igoso apho okanye egobileyo.”
  20,108,"Ngayo loo Mini abantu baya kulandela ngqongqo (ilizwi) lomkhwazi ka-Allâh, akukho bugoso-goso baya kuMbonisa bona. Kananjalo zonke (izandi) zamazwi ziya kuthobeka phambi koSolubabalo (uAllâh), yaye akukho nto uya kuyiva ngaphandle kwamazwi aphantsi ezingqi zeenyawo zabo"
  20,109,"Ngayo loo Mini akukho ntethelelo iya kunceda, ngaphandle kweyalowo uSolubabalo (uAllâh) Amnike imvume nelizwi lakhe liya kwamkeleka kuYe"
  20,110,"Yena (uAllâh) Uyakwazi okwenzekayo kuzo (izidalwa zaKhe) kweli hlabathi, noko kuza kwenzeka (kwilixa elisezayo) kodwa zona angekhe zibe nako ukuqulatha olo lwazi lwaKhe"
  20,111,"Kananjalo ubuso (babantu bonke) buya kuthotywa phambi (koAllâh), Ophila ngonaphakade, loWo Wondla, Akhusele konke okukhoyo. Akayi kuphumelela lowo uye wazithwalisa intswela bulungisa"
  20,112,"Kodwa yena lowo usebenza imisebenzi elungileyo, abe elikholwa akayi koyika (kwenzelwa) ntswela bulungisa nambandezelo"
  20,113,"Ngolo hlobo ke (umyalezo weThu) Siwuthumele phantsi uyi’Kur’ân yesiArabhu, Saza Sachaza ngengcaciso izilumkiso, khon’ukuze boyike uAllâh, okanye (ezizi lumkiso) zibe yinkumbuzo kubo"
  20,114,"Ngoko ke Uphakamile Yena ngaphezulu kuneento zonke uAllâh, uKumkani woKwenene. Ke kaloku musa ukungxama nge’Kur’ân ingekatyhilwa ngokupheleleyo isiTyhilelo sayo kuwe (Muhammad), yaye futhi wena yithi: “Nkosi yam! Ndongezelele ulwazi.”"
  20,115,"Ke kaloku Senza uMnqophiso noAdam ngaphambili, kodwa walibala yena, Samfumanisa engenako ukuzimisela"